{
  "stem": "7177.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The space was maybe-- I have to-- 50-- the-- the height was of course there, because it was the height of the basement.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the space that we were in was maybe [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] what should I say-- can I say 40, 50 centimeters, or 30 inches, something.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were standing up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were standing up, my sister and myself.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were standing up all night and having only a tiny little hole in the bottom of this space where we had to crawl through and which they had later on closed.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Only left a tiny little hole, so that if the Germans really came to the house to-- because somebody had told the Germans, yes, there were Jews in this particular house.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we-- they had Tima and his family had put wooden blocks in front of this tiny little hole and to make sure that the Germans wouldn't see the little hole.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Fortunately enough for us, the Germans did not come to the house.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we were OK that evening.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we-- we stayed in there most of the day.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was on a Saturday evening.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was January and-- oh no.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was January.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I think it was January 11, 1944.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was raining cats and dogs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was unheard of.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was very, very dark.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we had not been outside for almost a year.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Here is my sister, who can hardly see anything, and definitely cannot ride a bicycle at that time of day.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So here I was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I am 4' 11'.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that's not very tall.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I weigh a little bit more at the time, I think, but about what I weigh now, 85, 90 pounds.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
